Package gr.interamerican.wicket.callback

Interface Summary
CallbackAction Callback action.
ChainedCallbackAction Chain of responsibility enhancement of CallbackAction.
 

Class Summary
AbstractCallbackAction Abstract CallbackAction.
AbstractCommandCallback AbstractCommandCallback is a base class for command pattern based callbacks, namely callbacks that have a main execute() method.
AddElementToCollection<B extends Serializable> CallbackAction that adds an element to an indexed collection.
AddElementToCollectionI<B extends Serializable> CallbackAction that adds an element to an indexed collection.
AddElementToCollectionL<B extends Serializable> CallbackAction that adds an element to an indexed collection.
CallbackWrapper CallbackWrapper wraps another CallbackAction.
ChainedCallbackActionImpl Implementation of ChainedCallbackAction based on a Deque.
MethodBasedCallbackAction A MethodBasedCallbackAction is a Bo2WicketBlock that executes a method of its owner object.
RemoveElementFromCollection<B extends Serializable> CallbackAction that removes an element from a collection.
SimpleCallbackAction CallbackAction that executes an action that does not depend on the AjaxRequestTarget or the Form.
